{"tid":403105,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【澳門選戰】逼國籍寫「中國香港」 拒至少13記者入境","createTime":"2017-09-17T02:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T03:55:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e70a7971df0f9df61aff0e8984da6956b3b5f243","tid":403105,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T02:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170916/large/1505572402_461f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170916%2Flarge%2F1505572402_461f.png&h=12ccc901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 澳門立法會選舉吸引不少本港與外地傳媒赴澳採訪，不過當局如臨大敵，拒絕部份香港記者入澳，其中《蘋果》12名記者被拒入境。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》在過去一周先後派出多名記者去澳門採訪立法會選舉，最後共有12名文字及攝影記者遭澳門當局拒絕入境，有關記者均收到治安警察局發出的通知書，列明被拒入境原因是「對內部保安的穩定構成威脅」，《蘋果》記者被拒入境情況為近年最嚴重的一次。<br />\n<br />\n澳媒《愛瞞日報》早前亦報道，香港網媒「TMHK」一名記者上周五擬赴澳採訪，同樣被當局拒絕入境，該記者被要求填寫身份資料時在國籍一欄寫上「香港」，但治安警要求更正為「中國香港」，該記者被扣留約3小時後以「違反內部保安綱要法」為由遣返回港。<br />\n<br />\n香港記者協會主席楊健興表示，對於澳門當局屢次拒絕港媒入境的做法感到非常遺憾，他指記者採訪不會影響內部保安，但澳門每次有大新聞發生都拒絕港媒入境，他指上次風災發生同樣情況時已作出嚴正聲明，但澳門當局似乎對此漠視，記協擬向澳門政府再次反映有關問題之嚴重性。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170917/57219299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170917%2F57219299&d=a8jL8T0b4RR%2B4PsGv%2FxdOsKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=f50146d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170917%2F57219299&h=b9d111ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170917/57219299</a>"},{"pid":"231f75e48b95a25ea9e82511fc2471bf30f047d6","tid":403105,"uid":45635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:07:45.000Z","msg":"國籍填中國香港都錯啦，唔通叫中國香港國咩"},{"pid":"4fc8b436f19575a22c8237ad3386c2adf39808c0","tid":403105,"uid":121409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:09:32.000Z","msg":"澳門啲嘢報唔報都罷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1287a30548d757b48123629aae50cd28541e7c","tid":403105,"uid":127569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:38:04.000Z","msg":"咪撚報澳門d野啦，wfc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271104ff184857f0c751e99ddaad00465e5ec698","tid":403105,"uid":25183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:42:19.000Z","msg":"奶共奶到國籍係乜嘢意思都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06cc0e0684a6a103501ff7f38add5627f3489244","tid":403105,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:46:39.000Z","msg":"即是香港唔係國家，中國香港就係國家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a008aec2e651f530a12da73ac11787d87d1d3d0","tid":403105,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:52:32.000Z","msg":"由鳩佢啦<br />\n強國城市"},{"pid":"5f9da2086a1b288178022b90f6a4b4be8d4ca4b1","tid":403105,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T03:55:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>澳門啲嘢報唔報都罷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}